<AbstractNarration>This proposal is funded to reconstruct past sea surface temperatures and salinities in the sub-tropical Atlantic to determine if tropical forcing influenced climate oscillations associated with millennial scale changes.  d18O and Mg/Ca analyses of planktic foraminifera will be used to provide a robust estimate of these parameters at millennium to orbital time scales. &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;</AbstractNarration>
